This package takes care of the initial generation and preparation of MC data for the calorimeter project.

1. Generating/ generates MC files in ROOT format.
2. Converting/ converts these ROOT files to H5 format and also adds calculated features.
3. Filtering/ filters these samples and only saves the ones that we want to use for training.
4. Resampling/ re-emulates data as it would appear on a detector with different geometry.
